{"tid":865354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(左膠又嬴) 加拿大星期三開始大麻合法化","createTime":"2018-10-17T04:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T05:33:31.000Z","uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5907ef75a13435b89a9852a6679f1dcf39a4e943","tid":865354,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:00:52.000Z","msg":"把娛樂用大麻合法化列為競選承諾的加拿大總理杜魯道（Justin Trudeau）19日在推特上發文：「我們的孩子太容易獲取大麻了，罪犯也能輕易獲利，今天我們改變了這情況。」<br />\n<br />\n總理杜魯道在2015年競選期間就提出娛樂用大麻合法化，他認為加拿大禁止吸食大麻的法律，根本無法嚴格管制國民的吸食情形，導致加拿大的大麻黑市猖獗。2015年，加國人的大麻消費總額共計45億美元（約新台幣1360.4億元），相當於加國人購買紅酒的金額。聯邦政府推行大麻合法化就是希望，讓規模龐大的黑市大麻交易回到合法市場，便於政府的規管和控制，減少未成年人非法吸食大麻、從事與大麻相關的犯罪行為。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大參議院19日以52比29的票數通過了娛樂用大麻合法化，法案確立了大麻類物質的生產、銷售以及安全規範，不過出售大麻給未成年人仍屬刑事犯罪。加拿大總督批准後，最快今年9月就可以合法地於該國境內購買大麻。加拿大也將成為七國集團（G7）中第一個娛樂用大麻合法國，以及全球第二個全面開放大麻的國家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加拿大親友開始互傳whatsapp：<br />\n加拿大变左合法賣毒品國家，國旗應如上圖改。我地出門去其他地方實俾人搜到唔清唔楚。睇著日後有幾多年青人癡線，有幾多撞車因為吸左大麻。度魯多為在揾錢，為左討選票害死加拿大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2年前笑美國選侵侵  2年後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f9f7777494859eb534115a28365c5da947aa5d","tid":865354,"uid":119173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:01:38.000Z","msg":"遲d放假去加拿大上下太空先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eba2a7556b27e1a3a5f7da00b34c821c07ba109","tid":865354,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"一陣班友帶大麻去美國賣  侵侵當加拿大係墨西哥咁設過關限制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n左膠又嬴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何里活班仆街捨得去加拿大未？講左兩年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efa0cf2c0ee0a6353cccbed2c6aee82f1a60c10","tid":865354,"uid":19806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6eba2a7556b27e1a3a5f7da00b34c821c07ba109","tid":865354,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"一陣班友帶大麻去美國賣  侵侵當加拿大係墨西哥咁設過關限制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n左膠又嬴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何里活班仆街捨得去加拿大未？講左兩年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"美國都有州合法賣草 啲人都唔會帶去美國"}]}